Format: https://www.debian.org/doc/packaging-manuals/copyright-format/1.0/
Upstream-Name: snd-hda-codec-cs8409-imac
Source: https://github.com/petershevchenko/imac-sound
Comment:
 Apple iMac18,3 (CS42L83 / TAS5764) support for the in-kernel Cirrus Logic
 CS8409 HDA codec driver. Based on the mainline Linux CS8409 driver; the
 CS42L83 / TAS5764 register sequences were derived from the macOS AppleHDA
 driver via the GPL-2.0 out-of-tree project
 https://github.com/egorenar/snd-hda-codec-cs8409 .

